    <briefdescription>
<para>Software I2C (bit-banging) driver. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implements I2C master functionality using any two GPIO pins. Relies on <ref refid="syn__port__gpio_8h" kindref="compound">syn_port_gpio.h</ref> for pin manipulation. Uses a simple NOP loop for clock stretching/delays. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
